attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a shelf. The student starts by putting together the two sidebars and screwing them together. Then assembles the base of the shelf and mounts the sidebars onto it. The student tests to make sure everything is secure before continuing. They then mount the bottom tray onto the shelf and screw it in place. The student repeats this process for the middle and top trays. Finally, the student aligns the wheels of the shelf and screws them in place.
